# Mobile Color Implementation Guide

## ğŸ“± CloudScribble Mobile App Colors

This guide shows you how to implement CloudScribble's brand colors in your iOS and Android native apps.

## ğŸ iOS Implementation

### File Structure
```
ios/
â”œâ”€â”€ CloudScribble/
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Colors.swift          â† Your color definitions
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Assets.xcassets/
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ AppIcon.appiconset/
